Package com.komeetta.model

Class PurchaseOrder

java.lang.Object
com.komeetta.model.PurchaseOrder
@Entity public class PurchaseOrder extends Object
Represents a purchase order in the database. It has the following attributes: - orderId: the unique identifier of the order - supplier: the supplier from which the order was made - orderDate: the date and time when the order was placed - status: the status of the order (pending, in_progress, completed) - totalPrice: the total price of the order - items: a list of items in the order
